author: djames
msg: Upgrade Python default memory management to use one subpool per function call
so that separate variables can be garbage collected separately.
Include svn_pools.h, so that we can play with pools in svn_types.swg.
(svn_swig_py_pool_create_subpool): New SWIG macro. Creates a new default
(apr_pool_t): Use separate subpools for each function call.
(test_pool): Double check that our default pools are garbage collected
